Fully generic event bus system

UI emits event
-> EventBus.publish(event)
-> bus finds all subscribers/handlers
-> matching handlers run automatically
-> handlers may emit more events
-> more handlers may run

Compared to simple event-driven, it usually adds:

-> EventBus class
-> subscribe/unsubscribe mechanism
-> handler registry
-> event dispatch rules
-> possibly sync vs async handling
-> maybe event priorities
-> maybe chained events

